{"id":939,"date":"2021-01-04T14:10:09","date_gmt":"2021-01-04T14:10:09","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/?p=939"},"modified":"2021-01-04T14:10:09","modified_gmt":"2021-01-04T14:10:09","slug":"update-04-01-21","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/2021\/01\/04\/update-04-01-21\/","title":{"rendered":"Update (04\/01\/21)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>During the start of the Hachiman event, we were made aware of an issue that resulted in a number of players starting the event with scores carried over from a previous leaderboard.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Upon investigation, we determined that it would not be possible to retract these rewards, and we felt that it would be unfair to remove already-collected milestone rewards from player\u2019s accounts as the result of the bug.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We want to thank the community for reaching out to us with this issue, and we apologise for any inconvenience caused and thank you for your patience in waiting for a resolution.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To compensate for this issue, we are doing a number of things over the next few days. Firstly, we\u2019re launching a free bundle of rewards available to all players that contains:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>4* Boost Relic (<em>Forest Candle<\/em>)<\/li><li>3* Boost Relic (<em>Forest Candle<\/em>)<\/li><li>2* Boost Relic (<em>Forest Candle<\/em>)<\/li><li>1* Boost Relic (<em>Forest Candle<\/em>)<\/li><li>4* Titan XP Relic<\/li><li>4* Relic Shard<\/li><li>2x Epic Tokens<\/li><li>100 Portal Stones<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The Forest Candles will work as Boost Relics for the upcoming <em>Putrid Magic <\/em>Alliance War starting this Thursday 7th January. This bundle will be available to collect in-game within the next 24 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to this, we have made changes to the <em>Putrid Magic<\/em> Alliance War milestone rewards (marked in yellow):<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"461\" height=\"969\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Putrid_Rewards.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-940\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Putrid_Rewards.png 461w, https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/Putrid_Rewards-143x300.png 143w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 461px) 100vw, 461px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019ve gone through the reward track and doubled all instances of Gems and Divine Gems<strong>. <\/strong>The total number of Divine Gems is now <strong>1,000 <\/strong>and the total number of Gems is <strong>6,800.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Soul requirements for FINISH+ rewards have also been reduced from 25,000 to <strong>20,050 <\/strong>for the final reward.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Again, we want to thank you for your patience in waiting for this resolution and wish you all a happy new year. Stay safe, and we\u2019ll <em>see you on the battlefield<\/em>!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>DOT CONTENT CREATORS:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out some of the great DoT content creators and streamers across YouTube! Click the link on their names to go to their channels, and <strong>hit that subscribe button<\/strong> to get their latest videos as and when they drop:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCwS8gWrU26mj_C8DlwK_0WA\">ChefBaseGod<\/a> &#8211; Long time player and Discord-er returns with new content.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/churritto19\/videos\">_Churro_<\/a> &#8211; Live streams, update videos and after-show gatherings.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UC5S1d6IYSrt95MLKy4ITmMQ\/featured\">F2P Zeus<\/a> &#8211; Reactions, updates, battles, player profiles, Titan and Relic reviews.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCJ9s6BIyM7uUPJVAk7nbonw\">Vintage Plays<\/a> &#8211; DoT community conversations, overv